Are you ready for the ultimate Key West experience? Introducing Key West's Party Pass – the biggest and most valuable discount pass you'll ever need! With over $300 worth of free drinks, this pass is the key to unlocking an unforgettable time in paradise.
​
Say goodbye to overpriced drinks and hello to exclusive discounts at Key West's most popular bars. Get ready for a wild night out with free shots, free beers, and buy one get one free deals. But that's not all, the Party Pass will also take you off the beaten path to discover hidden gems and local hangouts that you might have missed out on.
​
Picture yourself sipping on a free shot at the island's only tutu bar – just one of the many perks of being a Party Pass owner. And the best part? The pass is instantly sent to your phone via text, so you can start saving immediately!
​
We've worked tirelessly to bring you exclusive deals with top establishments in Key West, so you can save BIG. With the average cost of one drink ranging from $8-$12, the Party Pass pays for itself at the first bar or restaurant. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to party like a VIP in Key West. Get your Party Pass today and let the good times roll!
​
Pass Details: Drink deals can be redeemed daily, which means you can visit all of the participating bars everyday you are in Key West on vacation & get another free drink.
